	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-06-26T01:36:13">Sherborne Investors (Guernsey) B Limited is a closed-ended investment company. The Company's investment objective is to realize capital growth from investment in a target company with the aim of generating a significant capital return for shareholders. The Company's investment policy is to invest in a company which is publicly quoted, most likely on one of the United Kingdom stock exchanges, which it considers to be undervalued as a result of operational deficiencies and which it believes can be rectified, thereby increasing the value of the investment. The Company invests in one target company at a time. Sherborne Investors Management (Guernsey) LLC is acting as the Investment Manager for the Company.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-02-22T08:35:37">BRIEF: For the six months ended 30 June 2015, Sherborne Investors (Guernsey) B Ltd revenues increased from L7.1M to L17.8M. Net income increased from L4.3M to L10.3M. Revenues reflect Unrealised gain on investment held at fa increase from -L14M to L14M, Dividend Income increase from L0K to L3.8M. Net income was partially offset by Administrative fees increase of 1% to L135K (expense). Dividend per share totaled to L0.38.</Text>
